---
import Layout from '@layouts/Layout.astro';
import { SITE } from '@lib/constants';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service"
  description="Terms of Service for Faithfully Crafted -- the rules and guidelines for using our website."
>
  <article class="py-12 sm:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 prose prose-sm sm:prose-base">
      <header class="text-center mb-12" data-reveal="up">
        <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-text">Terms of Service</h1>
        <p class="mt-3 text-text-muted">Last updated: March 13, 2026</p>
      </header>

      <section data-reveal="up" data-reveal-delay="100">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-text mt-10 mb-4">Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          By accessing and using the Faithfully Crafted website at
          <a href={SITE.url}>{SITE.url}</a> ("the Site"), you accept and agree to be bound by
          these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use the Site.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section data-reveal="up">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-text mt-10 mb-4">Description of Service</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          Faithfully Crafted is a portfolio and showcase website for handmade crochet creations.
          The Site displays gallery images, product information, and contact details. The Site is
          for informational and showcase purposes only.
        </p>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mt-3">
          The Site does not process payments, manage shopping carts, or handle transactions directly.
          All orders and inquiries are handled through third-party platforms such as Facebook
          Messenger, and are subject to the terms and policies of those platforms.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section data-reveal="up">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-text mt-10 mb-4">Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          All content on this Site -- including but not limited to photographs, images, text, logos,
          designs, and crochet patterns -- is the property of Faithfully Crafted or its content
          suppliers and is protected by applicable intellectual property laws.
        </p>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mt-3">
          You may not reproduce, distribute, modify, create derivative works from, publicly display,
          or commercially exploit any content from this Site without prior written permission from
          Faithfully Crafted.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section data-reveal="up">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-text mt-10 mb-4">User Conduct</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          When using this Site, you agree not to:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-muted mt-3 space-y-2">
          <li>Use the Site for any unlawful purpose or in violation of any applicable laws.</li>
          <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to any part of the Site or its systems.</li>
          <li>Interfere with or disrupt the integrity or performance of the Site.</li>
          <li>Scrape, crawl, or use automated means to access the Site beyond what is permitted by robots.txt.</li>
          <li>Copy, reproduce, or redistribute the Site's content without permission.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section data-reveal="up">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-text mt-10 mb-4">External Links</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          The Site contains links to third-party websites and services, including Facebook,
          Instagram, and Facebook Messenger. These links are provided for your convenience.
          We do not control and are not responsible for the content, privacy practices, or
          terms of service of any third-party sites. Accessing these links is at your own risk.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section data-reveal="up">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-text mt-10 mb-4">Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          The Site is provided on an "as is" and "as available" basis without warranties of any
          kind, either express or implied. We do not warrant that the Site will be uninterrupted,
          error-free, or free of harmful components.
        </p>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mt-3">
          Product images displayed on the Site are for illustrative purposes. Handmade items may
          vary slightly in color, size, and detail from the photographs shown.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section data-reveal="up">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-text mt-10 mb-4">Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          To the fullest extent permitted by applicable law, Faithfully Crafted shall not be
          liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages
          arising out of or related to your use of the Site, even if we have been advised of
          the possibility of such damages.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section data-reveal="up">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-text mt-10 mb-4">Governing Law</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          These Terms of Service are governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of
          the Republic of the Philippines. Any disputes arising from these terms shall be subject
          to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts located in Metro Manila, Philippines.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section data-reveal="up">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-text mt-10 mb-4">Changes to These Terms</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          We reserve the right to modify these Terms of Service at any time. Changes will be
          posted on this page with an updated "Last updated" date. Your continued use of the
          Site after any changes constitutes acceptance of the new terms.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section data-reveal="up">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-text mt-10 mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          If you have questions about these Terms of Service, you can reach us at:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-none text-text-muted mt-3 space-y-1">
          <li>Email: <a href={`mailto:${SITE.email}`}>{SITE.email}</a></li>
          <li>Facebook: <a href="https://www.facebook.com/gingerchets/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">facebook.com/gingerchets</a></li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
